english.segment1: Do you feel the tensions rise. Do you know why we always fight. To be better, better than you. And you better than me
english.segment2: I am not what you see, oh no. Not much more than a slave I wish to be. I am not what you see. Not much more a slave I should be. Nothing more, a slave I will be
english.segment3: How could I ever think to be more. than the one who created me. I watched him do all that he said, his words were. "Be a servant to all"
